00113 static void rna_DynamicPaintSurface_changePreview(Main *bmain, Scene *scene, PointerRNA *ptr)
00114 {
00115     DynamicPaintSurface *act_surface = (DynamicPaintSurface*)ptr->data;
00116     DynamicPaintSurface *surface = act_surface->canvas->surfaces.first;
00117 
00118     /* since only one color surface can show preview at time
00119      *  disable preview on other surfaces*/
00120     for (; surface; surface = surface->next) {
00121         if (surface != act_surface)
00122             surface->flags &= ~MOD_DPAINT_PREVIEW;
00123     }
00124     rna_DynamicPaint_redoModifier(bmain, scene, ptr);
00125 }

00155 static PointerRNA rna_PaintSurface_active_get(PointerRNA *ptr)
00156 {
00157     DynamicPaintCanvasSettings *canvas = (DynamicPaintCanvasSettings*)ptr->data;
00158     DynamicPaintSurface *surface = canvas->surfaces.first;
00159     int id = 0;
00160 
00161     for (; surface; surface = surface->next) {
00162         if (id == canvas->active_sur)
00163             return rna_pointer_inherit_refine(ptr, &RNA_DynamicPaintSurface, surface);
00164         id++;
00165     }
00166     return rna_pointer_inherit_refine(ptr, &RNA_DynamicPaintSurface, NULL);
00167 }

00197 /* uvlayer */
00198 static void rna_DynamicPaint_uvlayer_set(PointerRNA *ptr, const char *value)
00199 {
00200     DynamicPaintCanvasSettings *canvas = ((DynamicPaintSurface*)ptr->data)->canvas;
00201     DynamicPaintSurface *surface = canvas->surfaces.first;
00202     int id = 0;
00203 
00204     for (; surface; surface = surface->next) {
00205         if (id == canvas->active_sur) {
00206             rna_object_uvlayer_name_set(ptr, value, surface->uvlayer_name, sizeof(surface->uvlayer_name));
00207             return;
00208         }
00209         id++;
00210     }
00211 }

00228 static EnumPropertyItem *rna_DynamicPaint_surface_type_itemf(bContext *C, PointerRNA *ptr,
00229                                                              PropertyRNA *UNUSED(prop), int *free)
00230 {
00231     DynamicPaintSurface *surface = (DynamicPaintSurface*)ptr->data;
00232 
00233     EnumPropertyItem *item = NULL;
00234     EnumPropertyItem tmp = {0, "", 0, "", ""};
00235     int totitem = 0;
00236 
00237     /* Paint type - available for all formats */
00238     tmp.value = MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_T_PAINT;
00239     tmp.identifier = "PAINT";
00240     tmp.name = "Paint";
00241     RNA_enum_item_add(&item, &totitem, &tmp);
00242 
00243     /* Displace */
00244     if (surface->format == MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_F_VERTEX ||
00245         surface->format == MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_F_IMAGESEQ) {
00246         tmp.value = MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_T_DISPLACE;
00247         tmp.identifier = "DISPLACE";
00248         tmp.name = "Displace";
00249         RNA_enum_item_add(&item, &totitem, &tmp);
00250     }
00251 
00252     /* Weight */
00253     if (surface->format == MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_F_VERTEX) {
00254         tmp.value = MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_T_WEIGHT;
00255         tmp.identifier = "WEIGHT";
00256         tmp.name = "Weight";
00257         RNA_enum_item_add(&item, &totitem, &tmp);
00258     }
00259 
00260     /* Height waves */
00261     {
00262         tmp.value = MOD_DPAINT_SURFACE_T_WAVE;
00263         tmp.identifier = "WAVE";
00264         tmp.name = "Waves";
00265         RNA_enum_item_add(&item, &totitem, &tmp);
00266     }
00267 
00268     RNA_enum_item_end(&item, &totitem);
00269     *free = 1;
00270 
00271     return item;
00272 }
